result.title: Strange result from 2 submissions in 787B
result.content:
Hi,
I'm solving 787B, then submit solution and gave WA on test 7. After remove 1 line of code, it gaves AC. Still now, I don't understand why?
WA Submission: http://codeforces.com/contest/787/submission/25793357
 AC Submission: http://codeforces.com/contest/787/submission/25769844
 As you can see, the different between 2 submission is 'break', can you help me to find why I use 'break' it gaves WA.
Thank you!
